                                                                              \r\n					<h5>URL Keyword</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>&nbsp;User defined field for input of URL keywords, used for URL rewriting.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Available from</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined date field to input the date the product is available from. Date format is mm/dd/yy</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Active</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined field to mark a particular product as Active in the system or not. Possible inputs for this field are \'Yes\' &amp; \'No\'. Default value should be set as \'Yes\' to display products in the system.</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>COD Available</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined field to mark a particular product is available for cash on delivery in the system or not. Possible inputs for this field are \'Yes\' &amp; \'No\'. </p>                                        </li>                                                                              \r\n			</ul>                                </div>                            </div>                             \r\n	<div class=\"groups group-js\">                                 \r\n		<div class=\"group__head group__head-js\"> \r\n			<h5> Seller Products – Product Options</h5></div>                                 \r\n		<div class=\"group__body group__body-js\">                                     \r\n			<ul>                                                                      \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Seller Product Id</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined product identifier for the Product. This field needs to be the same as the seller product identifier defined in the Seller Product General Data sheet.    </p>                                        </li>                                          \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Option Identifier</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined unique identifier for the Option. This field needs to be the same as Option Identifier defined in Option export sheet. </p>                                        </li>                                          \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Option Value Identifier</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined unique identifier for the Option value. This field needs to be the same as Option Value Identifier defined in Option Value export sheet.</p>                                        </li>                                     \r\n			</ul>                                </div>                            </div>                             \r\n	<div class=\"groups group-js\">                                 \r\n		<div class=\"group__head group__head-js\"> \r\n			<h5> Seller Products – SEO</h5></div>                                 \r\n		<div class=\"group__body group__body-js\">                                     \r\n			<ul>                                                                      \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Seller Product Id </h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined product identifier for the Product. This field needs to be the same as the seller product identifier defined in the Seller Product General Data sheet.    </p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Meta Identifier</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined unique identifier for the Meta data. This works as a unique key for the system to identify a particular Meta data.</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Meta Title</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined input field for the user to define Meta title for the product. </p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Meta Keywords</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined input field for the user to define Meta keywords for the product.</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Meta Description</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined input field for the user to define Meta Description for the product.</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Other Meta Tags </h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined input field for the user to define other Meta tags for the product.</p>                                        </li>                                     \r\n			</ul>                                </div>                            </div>                             \r\n	<div class=\"groups group-js\">                                 \r\n		<div class=\"group__head group__head-js\"> \r\n			<h5> Seller Products – Special Price </h5></div>                                 \r\n		<div class=\"group__body group__body-js\">                                     \r\n			<ul>                                                                      \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Seller Product Id</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined product identifier for the Product. This field needs to be the same as the seller product identifier defined in the Seller Product General Data sheet.</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Start Date</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined date field to input the date from which the special price of the product starts from. Date format is mm/dd/yy</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>End Date</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined date field to input the date from which the special price of the product ends on. Date format is mm/dd/yy</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Price</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined field for special price of the product. </p>                                        </li>                                     \r\n			</ul>                                </div>                            </div>                             \r\n	<div class=\"groups group-js\">                                 \r\n		<div class=\"group__head group__head-js\"> \r\n			<h5> Seller Products – Volume Discount </h5></div>                                 \r\n		<div class=\"group__body group__body-js\">                                     \r\n			<ul>                                                                      \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Seller Product Id</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined product identifier for the Product. This field needs to be the same as the seller product identifier defined in the Seller Product General Data sheet.</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Min Quantity </h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined field for minimum quantity of the product to be purchased for volume discount.</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Discount Percentage </h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined field for discount percentage to be applied to the product in case of the volume discount. </p>                                        </li>                                     \r\n			</ul>                                </div>                            </div>                             \r\n	<div class=\"groups group-js\">                                 \r\n		<div class=\"group__head group__head-js\"> \r\n			<h5> Seller Products – Buy Together </h5></div>                                 \r\n		<div class=\"group__body group__body-js\">                                     \r\n			<ul>                                                                      \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Seller Product Id </h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined product identifier for the Product. This field needs to be the same as the seller product identifier defined in the Seller Product General Data sheet.</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Buy Together Selprod Id</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined product identifier for the buy together related Product. This field needs to be the same as the seller product identifier defined in the Seller Product General Data sheet.</p>                                        </li>                                     \r\n			</ul>                                </div>                            </div>                             \r\n	<div class=\"groups group-js\">                                 \r\n		<div class=\"group__head group__head-js\"> \r\n			<h5>  Seller Products – Related Products</h5></div>                                 \r\n		<div class=\"group__body group__body-js\">                                     \r\n			<ul>                                                                      \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Seller Product Id</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined product identifier for the Product. This field needs to be the same as the seller product identifier defined in the Seller Product General Data sheet.</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Related Selprod Id</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined product identifier for the related Products. This field needs to be the same as the seller product identifier defined in the Seller Product General Data sheet.  </p>                                        </li>                                     \r\n			</ul>                                </div>                            </div>                             \r\n	<div class=\"groups group-js\">                                 \r\n		<div class=\"group__head group__head-js\"> \r\n			<h5> Seller Products – Seller Product Policy </h5></div>                                 \r\n		<div class=\"group__body group__body-js\">                                     \r\n			<ul>                                                                      \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Seller Product Id</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined product identifier for the Product. This field needs to be the same as the seller product identifier defined in the Seller Product General Data sheet.</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Policy Point Identifier </h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p> User defined policy point identifier for the Product. This field needs to be the same as the policy point identifier defined on the Policy Points Management page under the CMS tab in the admin console. </p>                                        </li>                                     \r\n			</ul>                                </div>                            </div>                        </div>'),
